## Contribution Guidelines

By contributing to Protocol Security Architecture, you agree that:

1. Your contributions are dual-licensed under Apache 2.0 and MIT
2. You have the right to license your contributions
3. Your contributions don't violate third-party rights
4. You grant a patent license for your contributions (Apache 2.0)

